				<h2><center>RPCS3 (Playstation 3 Emulator) Setup</center></h2>
				<ol>
					<li>Download <a href="https://rpcs3.net/"><b>RPCS3</b></a>
					<li>Install a <a href="https://www.playstation.com/en-us/support/system-updates/ps3/"><b>PS3 firmware</b></a>
					<li>Install Persona 5 (and the DLC, if you have it).
					<li>Put your RAP file for Persona 5 in <i>RPCS3\dev_hdd0\home\00000001\exdata</i>
					<li>Navigate to <i>dev_hdd0\game\NPEB02436\USDIR</i> and move your downloaded <a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=14QgqisVDPsrfYzuhvEgKnMu61nWtCqsu"><b>mod.cpk</b></a> file inside
					<li>Replace the patch.yml file in the RPCS3 root folder with <b><a href="https://shrinefox.com/PatchCreator">this one</a></b>.
					<li>Start the game and enjoy!
				</ol>
